  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  19 &lt; age &lt; 60

          -  Refractory error stabled for at least one year

          -  No corneal pathology

          -  -3 &lt; bilateral myopia and astigmatism &lt; -5 with no difference more than 0.75 between 2
             eyes

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Keratoconus

          -  Ectatic corneal disease

          -  Glaucoma

          -  Corneal dystrophy

          -  Lens changes affecting the visual acuity

          -  Anterior or posterior uveitis

          -  Corneal scar
      </textblock>
